{"TopicId":153352,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Navball ghost marker","CreatedByName":"Skalou","CreatedById":133496,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-11T11:33:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Skalou","CreatedById":133496,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-11T11:33:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhi code modders,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is the \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#0000cd;\u0022\u003E\u003Cem\u003ENavball ghost marker\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/span\u003E great feature from the no more maintained mod\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/46454-10-enhanced-navball-13/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EEnhanced Navball\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022fhvpTtF.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/fhvpTtF.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nexample: Surface prograde and retrograde ghosting ( available for other all others markers too)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77210-ignath/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=http%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F46454-10-enhanced-navball-13%252F%2526page%253D13%2526csrfKey%253D6d225c985e17504194adc255a287d14d\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/77210-ignath/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 title=\u0022Go to Ignath\u0027s profile\u0022\u003EIgnath:\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGhosting displays the nodes that are \u0022behind\u0022 the navball. \u00A0They appear on the navball but are \u0022ghosted\u0022 (more faded than the nodes that are not \u0022behind\u0022 the navball)\u00A0out. \u00A0It makes things much easier to see exactly where your nodes are and where they are moving while you burn. \u00A0It may make it easier for you to follow a 45 degree burn between pro and normal, as it makes it easier to see where nodes are if they\u0027re not on the visible face of the navball.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI asked it to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161502\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161502-dizor/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dizor\u003C/a\u003E in his\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/139922-122-navballadjustor-v15-adjust-markers-scale-collapseafraid-behavior/#comment-2599330\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003ENavBallAdjustor\u003C/a\u003E mod thread where it could have been a great add-on feature, but he seems busy ( or not really interested? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope some of you (with codding skill i don\u0027t have) are missing this feature too. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dizor","CreatedById":161502,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-21T16:57:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nApparently there are no modders interested to implement ghost markers feature \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will have some free time on the eve of New Year, so i\u0027ll take a look how to add this feature to my NavBallAdjustor mod. I have an idea for this and will see if it work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Skalou","CreatedById":133496,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-21T18:58:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\namazing, you are the santa who\u00A0read my letter!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni don\u0027t code but tell me if i can help, test, etc... ( but not on my pc for 2 weeks)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}